Package swiftsolutions.cli.options

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CLIOption<T>
    Abstract class that represents a CLI option.
    CoresOption
    CLIOption that will determine whether the program will run in parallel, or sequential mode.
    HelpOption
    CLIOption that will tell the program whether or not to show the help messages.
    OutputOption
    CLIOption to determine whether the user wants a custom output name.
    VerboseOption
    CLIOption that determines whether the user wants to see debug messages.
    VisualizeOption
    CLIOption to determine whether the user wants to see the visualized version of the algorithm running inside the GUI
